# Insertion {#insertion}

Prox. phalanx of 1st toe @gilroyAtlasAnatomy2020

# Nerve

[Deep Fibular N.]({{< var ref-deep-fibular-nerve.path >}}) ([L5]({{< var ref-nerve-root.l5 >}}), [S1]({{< var ref-nerve-root.s1 >}})) @gilroyAtlasAnatomy2020

